title: Marilyn Manson & The Spooky Kids Volume I & II (FLAC)
description:
Marilyn Manson & The Spooky Kids Volume I & II

This was a request from some ETS peeps who told me these albums were not currently available in FLAC, so thank them if this is something you needed/wanted.

Both albums were ripped from the original CDs that Scott Putesky sent me.

Volume I: Bitchy Beginnings
Earliest authentic demos of Marilyn Manson & The Spooky Kids 1990-1992
1. My Monkey
2. Son Of Man
3. No Class (Styrofoam Raps)
4. Bitchy Beginnings Of An Oversexed 12 Year Old
5. Cake & Sodomy
6. (Strange Same) Dogma
7. Let Your Ego Die .... 2 track, live in rehearsal
8. My Monkey .... 16 track/Sync Studios
9. Phone Message (Jen)
10. She's Not My Girlfriend
11. White Knuckles .... 16 track/Sync Studios
all recordings are 4-track except where noted
produced by Scott Putesky for Psychic Theater
